            "title": "特步主品牌上季零售銷售錄低單位數增長 索康尼品牌則按年升逾20%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">特步國際(01368)公布，特步主品牌於上季零售銷售錄得低單位數按年增長，零售折扣水平介乎七折至七五折，渠道庫存週轉約4個半月。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">至於索康尼品牌，期內零售銷售則錄得按年增長超過20%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15898606-%e7%89%b9%e6%ad%a5%e4%b8%bb%e5%93%81%e7%89%8c%e4%b8%8a%e5%ad%a3%e9%9b%b6%e5%94%ae%e9%8a%b7%e5%94%ae%e9%8c%84%e4%bd%8e%e5%96%ae%e4%bd%8d%e6%95%b8%e5%a2%9e%e9%95%b7-%e7%b4%a2%e5%ba%b7%e5%b0%bc%e5%93%81",
